items.name: case notSet
items.desc: A constant indicating that either the user’s biological sex characteristic type is not set, or the user has not granted your app permission to read that characteristic type.

items.name: case female
items.desc: A constant indicating that the user is female.

items.name: case male
items.desc: A constant indicating that the user is male.

items.name: case other
items.desc: A constant indicating that the user is otherwise not categorized as either male or female.
